title: Community comes together to kick off annual Angels’ Night volunteer campaign (City of Detroit, MI) ...
text: ( Source : City of Detroit , MI) Mayor Mike Duggan joined today with an array of civic, community and business leaders at the Ladder 6 Fire Station on Detroit 's lower east side to call on residents to volunteer for this year's Angels' Night
